longBusinessSummary: EMS Limited constructs, designs, and installs water, wastewater, and domestic waste treatment facilities in India. The company offers turnkey services in water and wastewater collection, treatment, disposal, and manufactures own items which are used for construction purposes. EMS Limited was founded in 1998 and is based in Ghaziabad, India.
